Package pl.pz1.poker.moves

Interface Move

All Known Implementing Classes:
Call, Exchange, Exit, Fold, Join, NewGame, Raise, Status
public interface Move
The Move interface defines the contract for all poker game moves. Each move must implement the execute method to define its behavior.

  • Method Summary

    Modifier and Type
    Method
    Description
    String
    execute(Game game, Player player, String parameters)
    Executes the move in the context of the game and player.

  • Method Details

    • execute

      String execute(Game game, Player player, String parameters)
      Executes the move in the context of the game and player.
      Parameters:
      game - the current game instance.
      player - the player making the move.
      parameters - additional parameters required for the move.
      Returns:
      a message indicating the outcome of the move.
